 At Least $20 Billion Needed for Highway Work: Experts at an international 
seminar on roads and bridges estimated that the nation needs between $20 
billion and $25 billion to rebuild its road system, the Vietnam News Agency 
reported.Almost half of Vietnam's 66,000 miles of roads have been rated poor by 
