<DOCNO> LA013194-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 008822 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 31, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 16; Column 1; Metro Desk 
