<TEXT>
<P>
 Restaurant Unharmed -- Contrary to a report in Sunday's Calendar, the 
hamburger restaurant Johnny Rockets on Ventura Boulevard in Encino was not 
damaged by the Jan. 17 earthquake and is open. However, another Johnny Rockets 
restaurant on Ventura Boulevard in Sherman Oaks is closed due to earthquake 
damage. 
</P>
